        <Parent_String>nations [300128207], sovereign states [300232420], political administrative bodies by degree of independence [300232417], political administrative bodies [300261086], administrative bodies [300000768], organizations (groups) [300025948], Organizations (hierarchy name) [300234770], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
